description: This is a JavaScript source file serving as the entry point for a React web application. It imports React and ReactDOM libraries, along with local CSS styles and the main App component. It initializes the React application by rendering the App component inside a DOM element with the ID 'root' using ReactDOM's createRoot method.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components within the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the React root created.
